{"tid":759304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯國家杜馬通過議案冀剌激遠東濱海邊疆區經濟投資","createTime":"2018-07-28T13:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T13:54:40.000Z","uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a12371a064728ad08e775f871cbb8ac4008fca8a","tid":759304,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T13:10:54.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯國家杜馬通過在遠東濱海邊疆區，設立經濟區。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯國會下議院通過的法律草案，將按設立特別行政區的需要，對俄羅斯現行國際公司法、民法典、稅法典、外匯管制法、商船航行法及其他法律進行調整。特別行政區內在稅收、外匯監管和僱用外來勞動力等方面提供優惠，創造有利營商環境和提高當地投資活力，促進濱海邊疆區至整個遠東地區發展。<br />\n<br />\n法案將送交國會上議院審議。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯近年大力實施遠東開發戰略，積極建設符茲華托克（海參崴）自由港和一系列跨越式開發區，採取優惠措施吸引投資者投資遠東地區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1409321-20180728.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1409321-20180728.htm&d=lSILiO91gCnBUF%2B6whAwRF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=ddd1cb2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1409321-20180728.htm&h=89c92828\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1409321-20180728.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d32ad79283e659d93776723b97f99f9b36cbdf43","tid":759304,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T13:27:47.000Z","msg":"中國領土神聖不可侵犯, 傅振中入黎講俾大家知幾時先收復威海衛?"},{"pid":"bce9651f0e9078ea4557c5be0026f0541455ecf6","tid":759304,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d32ad79283e659d93776723b97f99f9b36cbdf43","tid":759304,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T13:27:47.000Z","msg":"中國領土神聖不可侵犯, 傅振中入黎講俾大家知幾時先收復威海衛?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T13:48:04.000Z","msg":"威海衛喺山東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d78c0c6d986a8be6f81beabbb1e0120bafcb6f77","tid":759304,"uid":42767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bce9651f0e9078ea4557c5be0026f0541455ecf6","tid":759304,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike